		<article class="obj_article_details">
	<h1 class="page_title">
		Enhancing Portal System Resilience with a Modified Lion Optimization Algorithm (MLOA) for Cyber Threat Detection
	</h1>

	
	<div class="row">
		<div class="main_entry">

							<ul class="item authors">
