				</span>
				<span class="value">
																		Anomaly Detection, 													Cybersecurity, 													Modified Lion Optimization Algorithm, 													Nature-Inspired Algorithms, 													Performance Metrics, 													Portal Systems, 													SSC-OCSVM, 													UNSW-NB15 Dataset															</span>
